{"title":"本部浴池","shareable":true,"id":"guide/bath/benbu","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"title","text":"简介"},{"tag":"text","text":["本部学生浴池在八舍南侧，一楼是男宾、二楼是女宾。","浴池一楼同时包含奶茶店、水果店、理发店、眼镜店、烘焙店、洗衣店等店铺，同时还包含了休息室、健身器材等设施。"]},{"tag":"location","title":"本部浴池","points":[{"latitude":43.86249,"longitude":125.337057}]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-main.jpg","desc":"正门","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-outside.jpg","desc":"外景","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-main-2.jpg","desc":"大厅","watermark":true},{"tag":"text","heading":"一楼","text":["拥有水果店、复印店、奶茶店、化妆品店、理发店等店铺","包含健身房与休息室等设施。","还有一个小小的男宾😑"]},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"本部浴池生活区","path":"guide/life/benbu-bath-district"}]},{"tag":"carousel","images":["https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-left.jpg","https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-right.jpg","https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-shop3.jpg","https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-shop4.jpg"]},{"tag":"text","heading":"二楼","text":["浴池二楼为女宾区。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"洗浴区域"},{"tag":"p","text":["洗浴区在入口处提供了吹风机、梳妆镜、体重秤等设置。","每个洗浴间都有可上锁的门，周围是毛玻璃，门后有放置衣服和鞋子的箱子。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-env.jpg","desc":"洗浴区","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-cloth-box.jpg","desc":"衣物箱","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-dressing-table.jpg","desc":"梳妆台 (有吹风机)","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"https://assets.innenu.com/img/bath/benbu-scale.jpg","desc":"体重秤","watermark":true},{"tag":"title","text":"开放时间"},{"tag":"text","text":["8:00🕗 - 22:00🕙","每月 15 日、30 日上午检修"]},{"tag":"title","text":"校外浴池"},{"tag":"p","text":["三舍东边就是吉林省雪立方摩尔运动中心有限公司，内部洗浴条件很不错，有隔间，带学生证可以打折，价格是洗浴 ￥18/人，搓澡 ￥12/人。"]}],"time":"2023 年 7 月 16 日 19:41:46"}